---
import Lysknap from "../components/Lysknap.astro";
import Lyssingle from "../components/Lyssingle.astro";
---



<div class="baggrund">
    <img src="sunsetgarden.jpeg" alt="Sunset Garden">
    <div class="tekst">
        <li style="--farve:#ffdd1c">
            <a href="#" data-text="&nbsp;Sunset&nbsp;Garden">&nbsp;Sunset Garden</a>
        </li>
        <div class="h2">
            <h2>WHO: The Lightning Guys</h2>
            <h2>Where: Vestre Kirkegaard</h2>
        </div>
        <Lyssingle />
    </div>
</div>

<div class="center-container" id="center-container">
    <div class="container">
        <p>Vestre Kirkegård is the largest cemetery in Denmark, and home to a wide variety of burial sites. You will find Catholic, Muslim, Jewish, Faeroese, Greenlandic and several other areas here.</p>
        <p>This light installation represents the setting sun, a metaphor for death, or the rising sun and new beginnings. Those Guys Lighting are a group of young light designers and engineers from Riga, Latvia, who previously participated in Copenhagen Light Festival in 2022 with their interactive installation “On the Wave of Light” along Sydbanestien in Sydhavnen.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="billede">
    <img src="sunsetgarden.jpeg" alt="Sunset Garden">
</div>

    <style> 

     .baggrund {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 100vw;
            height: 80vh;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .baggrund img {
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            filter: blur(10px);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .tekst {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: -33rem;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        li {
            position: relative;
            list-style: none;
        }

        li a {
            position: relative;
            font-size: 3.3em;
            text-decoration: none;
            line-height: 2;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: transparent;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1.4px white;
            font-family: lato, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        li a::before {
            content: attr(data-text);
            position: absolute;
            color: var(--farve);
            width: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: 0.75s;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--farve);
        }

        li a:hover::before {
            width: 100%;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 25px var(--farve));
            cursor: none;
        }

        .h2 {
            color: var(--glow-color);
        }

        /* Container for text content */
        .center-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Image container */
        .billede {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 12rem;
        }

        .billede img {
            width: 65vw;
            animation: border-flicker1 3.5s linear infinite;
        }

        .billede img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.15);
            transition: 0.7s;
        }

        @keyframes border-flicker1 {
            0%, 4%, 100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            2%, 30% {
                opacity: 1.8;
            }
            8%, 70% {
                opacity: 0.9;
            }
        }

        /* Media query for screens with a max-width of 768px (typical tablet size) */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      

            .center-container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            li a {
              font-size: 2.9rem;
            }
        }



    
    </style>